data.description: Step into the warmth of this charming 3-bed, 1.5-bath cottage home at 211 Bernard Ave, AMA, LA 70031. This home, spread across two lots measuring 70 x 204, has plenty of updates including newer windows, roof, attic insulation, and a hot water heater. The heart of the home is an inviting open kitchen and dining area. The three bedrooms offer not just  space but also an abundance of natural light, and the primary bedroom has its own convenient half bath. There is a 21 x 20 detached 2 car shed. Enjoy the perks of this prime location, many amenities, top schools, and dining and shopping options!
